- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a possible category as the paper discusses the robustness of homology classes under perturbations of the function, which is a common topic in control theory and system analysis.
- cs.GR (Graphics) is a possible category as the paper mentions the applications of the results in scientific visualization, which is a common topic in computer graphics.
